These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-4-1::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: white, azure, green, ebony, purple
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: october, january, july, august, march
5 different games are played: domino, whist, monopoly, scrabble, snooker
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: poppy, begonia, azalea, zinnia, tulip
 1. the person who growsazalea is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in march##3
 2. the person who's birthday is in october is in an odd position##4
 3. the person playing domino is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
 4. the person who likes purple is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
 5. the person who likes white is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in october##3
 6. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person who likes white##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
 8. the person who growstulip is in an even position##4
 9. the person who growspoppy is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3
10. the person playing monopoly is the person who's birthday is in july##1
11. the person playing whist is on the left of the person who likes azure##1
12. the person who likes purple is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in october##3
13. the person who likes purple is on the right of the person who growsbegonia##1
14. the person who growstulip is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
15. the person playing scrabble is the person who likes ebony##1
16. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person who likes white##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |        2        |     3      |    4     |     5     |
| Color      | green    | white   | ebony     | purple      | azure      |
| Birthday           | july | march | october    | august | january |
| Game   | monopoly       | domino         | scrabble      | whist      | snooker    |
| Flower   | azalea    | zinnia         | begonia | tulip  | poppy   |

