.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-4-2::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: september, april, october, february, august
There are 5 different favourite colors: grey, white, ebony, red, chestnut
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: orchid, azalea, amaryllis, lily, daisy
5 different games are played: backgammon, scrabble, chess, monopoly, go
 1. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the person playing monopoly##3
 2. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who likes grey##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in october is the person who likes chestnut##1
 4. the person who growslily is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 5. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the person playing go##1
 6. the person who likes ebony is in an odd position##4
 7. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left or right of the person who growsazalea##3
 8. the person who's birthday is in april is between the person who's birthday is in october and the person playing backgammon##2
 9. the person who growsorchid is on the left or right of the person who likes white##3
10. the person who growsorchid is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in september##3
11. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
12. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left or right of the person who likes ebony##3
13. the person who growsdaisy is on the left or right of the person playing chess##3
14. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |      5      |
| Birthday         | february | april | october   | september | august |
| Color   | ebony      | white   | chestnut    | grey        | red        |
| Flower           | lily         | daisy  | orchid  | azalea   | amaryllis      |
| Game     | backgammon        | monopoly  | chess | go | scrabble         |

