.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-4-3::.
City: edinburgh, colone, new-york, hannover, boston
There are 5 different favourite colors: blood-red, brown, coral, fuchsia, yellow
House: cottage, art-deco, tower, townhouse, gothic-revival
There 5 different types of food: cabbage, kiwi, plum, kale, blueberry
 1. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the townhouse house##1
 2. the cottage house is on the left of the person who likes fuchsia##1
 3. the person who likes brown is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
 4. the person traveling to hannover is the person traveling to hannover##1
 5. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the townhouse house##1
 6. the person who likes coral is on the right of the person who likes brown##1
 7. the tower house is on the far right##1
 8. the person eating plum is on the left or right of the person eating blueberry##3
 9. the person who likes fuchsia is the person eating plum##1
10. the person traveling to edinburgh is the art-deco house##1
11. the person eating kale is the person traveling to boston##1
12. the art-deco house is between the person eating kiwi and the person who likes blood-red##2
13. the person who likes blood-red is on the left or right of the person traveling to edinburgh##3
14. the gothic-revival house is on the far left or far right##3
15. the person traveling to boston is in an odd position##4
16. the person traveling to colone is on the left or right of the person traveling to hannover##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |    3     |      4       |       5       |
