 2. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far right##1
 3. the person playing go is on the left of the person playing domino##1
 4. the person who likes light-blue is in an odd position##4
 5. the person traveling to london is on the left or right of the person traveling to boston##3
 6. the person who likes coral is the person playing snooker##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who likes azure##1
 8. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left or right of the person who likes orange##3
 9. the person playing billiard is the person traveling to nizza##1
10. the person who's birthday is in march is in an odd position##4
11. the person traveling to boston is on the far left##1
12. the person who likes light-blue is on the far left or far right##3
13. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
14. the person playing snooker is the person playing snooker##1
15. the person who likes white is the person who's birthday is in november##1
16. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
17. the person playing go is on the left or right of the person who likes azure##3

