.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-4-5::.
5 different pets are kept: goat, rabbit, pony, hedgehog, bird
The people have 5 different hobbies: cooking, photography, fishing, card-games, skydiving
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: documentary, sports, horror, epic, adventure
The people have 5 different jobs:  dancer, social-worker, analyst, designer, writer
 1. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
 2. the person watching horror movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is cooking##3
 3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the far left##1
 4. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
 5. the person watching sports movies is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the owner of the bird is in an odd position##4
 7. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the owner of the goat##3
 8. the owner of the pony is between the owner of the rabbit and the analyst##2
 9. the dancer is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is photography##3
10. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
11. the social-worker is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
12. the designer is on the right of the analyst##1
13. the owner of the goat is the person watching documentary movies##1
14. the owner of the pony is on the right of the analyst##1
15. the writer is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
16. the owner of the rabbit is the person who's hobby is cooking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3      |     4      |       5       |
| Pet      | bird       | hedgehog  | goat        | pony   | rabbit          |
| Hobby   | skydiving    | card-games | fishing  | photography    | cooking     |
| Movie-Genre         | sports      | adventure | documentary | horror | epic |
| Job     | social-worker | writer    | analyst | designer       | dancer           |

