5 different games are played: go, scrabble, poker, billiard, canasta
5 different pets are kept: hedgehog, goat, guinea-pig, hamster, snake
There are 5 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, fanta, mirinda, iced-tea, almond-milk
 1. the person drinking fanta is the owner of the snake##1
 2. the owner of the snake is in an odd position##4
 3. the person playing go is on the left or right of the owner of the guinea-pig##3
 4. the person playing poker is the owner of the goat##1
 5. the person playing canasta is on the left or right of the person playing billiard##3
 6. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 7. the person who likes blood-red is the owner of the goat##1
 8. the person playing go is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
 9. the person playing go is the person drinking mirinda##1
10. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
11. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left##1
12. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left or right of the person playing billiard##3
13. the person who likes red is in an odd position##4
14. the person who likes purple is on the left or right of the owner of the hamster##3
15. the person who likes purple is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
16. the person playing go is in an odd position##4
17. the owner of the hamster is the person drinking mirinda##1
18. the person who likes azure is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |       4        |     5      |
