 2. the person who likes emerald is on the left or right of the person who likes yellow##3
 3. the person who likes emerald is on the left or right of the person who likes yellow##3
 4. the person who's hobby is hiking is in an even position##4
 5. the fan of punk is on the far left##1
 6. the victorian house is between the fan of classical and the wooden house##2
 7. the fan of reggae is between the fan of folk and the farmhouse house##2
 8. the craftsman house is the craftsman house##1
 9. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the fan of punk##1
10. the person who's hobby is dancing is in the middle##1
11. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who likes black##1
12. the fan of punk is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
13. the wooden house is on the left or right of the ranch-style house##3
14. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the fan of punk##1
15. the farmhouse house is on the right of the person who likes purple##1
16. the person who likes yellow is on the far right##1

