.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-4-15::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, dannemann, bolivar, chaman, bluemaster
There are 5 different favourite beverages: mirinda, coffee, milk, water, soy-milk
City: hannover, boston, prague, venice, new-york
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: zinnia, iris, dahlia, orchid, tulip
 1. the dannemann-smoker is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
 2. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the person who growszinnia##3
 3. the person traveling to hannover is on the left or right of the person traveling to prague##3
 4. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1
 5. the person drinking water is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1
 6. the person who growsorchid is in an even position##4
 7. the person who growszinnia is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
 8. the person traveling to boston is between the person who growsdahlia and the bluemaster-smoker##2
 9. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
10. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person traveling to prague##3
11. the person drinking mirinda is in an odd position##4
12. the person who growsiris is on the far right##1
13. the chaman-smoker is on the far right##1
